{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"81108d63e7","title":"周恩来就限期收回被抢武器对新疆军区的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3501299bb3","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"81108d63e7"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"ee21afb82f","name":"新疆文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fe60c0f369","type":"title","text":"周恩来就限期收回被抢武器对新疆军区的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7"},{"id":"de1a0a89cf","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7"},{"id":"e55e95a87e","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：八点十分〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7"},{"id":"f6304441f3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理办公室周家鼎同志传达总理指示：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7"},{"id":"5d0d5bf6c5","type":"paragraph","text":"三促最近抢枪很凶，总理让我告诉军区，让郭鹏同志对三促做工作，所抢的武器要限期收回，全部交回，否则要通报全国。这种做法是违反《九 · 五》命令的，是不允许的。限期交回（期限 总理没有讲，请军区考虑），否则要通报全国，一通报，他们就要垮台。据说，三促几次冲击空九军。代表都在这里，有什么问题不能解决？为什么要这样搞？总理说：请军区出面谈。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7"},{"id":"bfc16daef5","type":"paragraph","text":"周家鼎同志说：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7"},{"id":"dd0a0a978b","type":"paragraph","text":"这是总理指示，你就这样转告军区首长。总理要我直接告诉郭鹏同志，请你转告一下。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7"}],"page":{"id":"d7792e8707","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"81108d63e7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}